  "title": "마음 따뜻하신 환자분들",
  "addDate": "2014. 11. 26.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220192480567",
  "html_size": 182266,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220192480567\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220192480567\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/91b902ea458288bc.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"726\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 726px;\" id=\"20141126_94/isuhani_1416975391013bjBSm_JPEG/PB263729.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033447E9D37')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/91b902ea458288bc.jpg\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">대전에서 한달에 3~4번씩은 오셔서 추나 치료받는 환자분 따님께서 사다주셨어요.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">어머니께서 대전에서 오시는것도 일이고 힘드신데,</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오실때마다 항상 잘 챙겨주시고 신경써드려서 감사하다 하시면서 사다주신거에요.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">저희가 당연히 해야할일을 했을뿐인데..</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img id=\"se_object_141697568312645145\" src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/sticker/pc/moon_and_james/original/1.png\" class=\"__se_object_invalid\" jsonvalue=\"%7B%22stickerCode%22%20%3A%20%22moon_and_james-1%22%7D\" alt=\"moon_and_james-1\" /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">박스에 Merry Christmas라고만 저혀있어서&nbsp;어떤빵인가 궁굼해서 열어보았는데,<br />짜잔~~~ 맛있는 녹차 카스테라랍니다.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20141126_268/isuhani_1416975432353WpqpH_JPEG/PB263727.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"416\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 416px;\" id=\"20141126_268/isuhani_1416975432353WpqpH_JPEG/PB263727.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033447E9D37')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20141126_268/isuhani_1416975432353WpqpH_JPEG/PB263727.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">빵이.. 너무 촉촉해서 맛있어보이죠? </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">(저는 개인적으로 파리바게트 녹차 카스테라 완전 좋아합니다ㅋ)</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">우리&nbsp;환자분들은 무언가를&nbsp;주시면, </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">꼭 맛있고 좋은것만 주시는거 같아요 헤헤 ^^</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9b6bf9af7e36f747.jpg\" width=\"548\" height=\"414\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 548px; rheight: 414px;\" id=\"20141126_140/isuhani_1416978378278ewHLF_JPEG/PB263726.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033447E9D37')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9b6bf9af7e36f747.jpg\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">저희 환자분들은 한분 한분 모두 마음 따뜻하신분들만 계신거같아요.. </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오실때마다 모두 밝게 웃어주시고</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">모두 다 가족같은 분이세요.. </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">맛있는 빵 잘먹겠습니다 ^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img id=\"se_object_141697832316099979\" src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/sticker/pc/line_characters_in_love/original/31.png\" class=\"__se_object_invalid\" style=\"border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 164px; height: 151px;\" width=\"164\" height=\"151\" jsonvalue=\"%7B%22stickerCode%22%20%3A%20%22line_characters_in_love-31%22%7D\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-31\" /><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
